ActsAsMostPopular
=================

Makes your models feel like they are in high school again.  This plugin retrieves
model objects with the most popular values for each column.  It adds methods of
the form most_popular_column_name.  You can control how many results you get with
the :limit option.  The default limit is 5.

Usage
=====

class Exercise < ActiveRecord::Base
	acts_as_most_popular
end

class YourController < ActionController::Base
	def index
		@popular_exercises = Exercise.most_popular_names
	end
end

